#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:2
msgid "接线"
msgstr "Wiring"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:8
msgid "接线注意事项"
msgstr "Wiring Precautions"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:9
msgid "进行接线操作时，应严格遵循如下要求："
msgstr ""
"When performing wiring operations, the following requirements must be "
"strictly followed:"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:16
msgid "名称：**警告**"
msgstr "Name: **Warning**"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:18
#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:87
msgid "说明："
msgstr "Instructions:"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:20
msgid "请勿触摸手臂基座内部关节模组器件，以免发生触电危险。"
msgstr ""
"Do not touch the internal joint module components of the arm base to avoid "
"electric shock hazard."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:21
msgid "外部接线工作仅限经过培训并授权的合格工程师来完成。"
msgstr ""
"Only trained and authorized qualified engineers are allowed to perform "
"external wiring work."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:22
msgid "通电前需检查设备的电压等级，否则可能造成人员伤亡和设备损坏。"
msgstr ""
"Before powering on, check the voltage level of the equipment; otherwise, it "
"may cause personal injury and equipment damage."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:23
msgid "为保证安全，设备必须可靠接地。"
msgstr "To ensure safety, the equipment must be reliably grounded."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:24
msgid "除电源接头外，严禁将电源输入端接入到其他端子，否则可能会损坏产品。"
msgstr ""
"Do not connect the power input terminal to any other terminal except the "
"power connector, otherwise the product may be damaged."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:25
msgid "所有端子接入的输入电压严禁超出允许范围。"
msgstr ""
"The input voltage connected to all terminals must not exceed the allowable "
"range."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:26
msgid "通电前需确保接线线序正确，连接可靠、绝缘可靠，否则可能会损坏产品。"
msgstr ""
"Ensure the wiring sequence is correct, the connection is reliable and the "
"insulation is reliable before power is applied, otherwise the product may be"
" damaged."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:29
msgid "系统接线"
msgstr "System wiring"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:30
msgid ""
"人形机械臂ART3-R7共有四种配置：配置一为单臂，配置二为单臂+控制器，配置三为双臂，配置四为双臂+控制器+分支器。其接线图如图4-1、4-2、4-3和4-4所示。"
msgstr ""
"The humanoid robotic arm ART3-R7 has four configurations: configuration one "
"is a single arm, configuration two is a single arm plus a controller, "
"configuration three is dual arms, and configuration four is dual arms plus a"
" controller and a brancher. Its wiring diagrams are shown in Figures 4-1, "
"4-2, 4-3, and 4-4."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:32
msgid "人形机械臂ART3-R7的供电电压为DC48V，控制器和分支器的供电电压为DC24V，如图4-5和4-6所示。"
msgstr ""
"The power supply voltage of the humanoid robotic arm ART3-R7 is DC48V, and "
"the power supply voltage of the controller and the brancher is DC24V, as "
"shown in Figure 4-5 and 4-6."

