#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:71
msgid "上位机调试接线"
msgstr "Host computer debugging wiring"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_line.rst:72
msgid "调试机械臂时用网线连接上位机和控制器。如图4-7所示。"
msgstr ""
"When debugging the robotic arm, connect the host computer and controller "
"with an Ethernet cable, as shown in Figure 4-7."

